name: Pixel
description: Meet Pixel, a phone by Google. It’s the first phone with the Google Assistant built in. Ask it questions. Tell it to do things. It’s your own personal Google Assistant, always ready to help. The 12.3MP rear camera and 8MP front camera take stunning photos in low light, bright light, or any light. And with unlimited storage for your photos and videos, you’ll never have to delete an old memory to make room for a new one. Additional features for Pixel include a 5.0” AMOLED display, cinematic widescreen 16:9 aspect ratio, Corning Gorilla Glass for durability, and more

name: Vertu Signature
description: Meticulously handcrafted from the finest rare materials to the label's uncompromising standards, Signature is the outstanding, elementary expression of Vertu’s vision.

name: Studio Selfie 2
description: Meet the Studio Selfie 2, the new and improved Selfie smartphone with vast improvements in design, build quality, and battery life. Your movies and pictures will look amazing on the fully laminated 5inch display with BLU Infinite View (IPS) and BLU Next Lens Technologies (OGS). Take the best pictures ever with your 5 Megapixel Main Camera with Auto-focus or get your Selfie on with the 5 Megapixel Front Camera.

name: PRIV
description: PRIV combines everything you expect from BlackBerry plus the full eco-system of Android and its apps. PRIV comes with added security to let you know when your data could be at risk, so you can take action to improve it.

name: Liquid
description: The Z220 features a design that is as functional as it is beautiful. The fabric-inspired motif on the rear cover creates a look of sophistication and adds surface texture. The silver middle frame features a unique square pyramid design. Besides being great to look at, this styling also makes the device easier to grip and use with one hand.
